flowchart LR
    I[Idea]
    R[Research]
    V[Vision]
    S[Strategy]
    T[Task Brainstorm]
    G1{Gate 1\nStrategy fixed?}
    D[Dependency Sort]
    P[Phase Design]
    G2{Gate 2\nExecution plan fixed?}
    E[Execute]
    Gen[Generator]
    Ev[Evaluator]
    TD[Task Done]
    RP[Review Pool]
    HG[Human Gate]
    PG{Phase Gate}
    C[Complete]

    I --> R
    R --> V
    V --> S
    S --> R
    S --> T
    T --> S

    S --> G1
    G1 -- reject --> R
    G1 -- approve --> D

    D --> P
    P --> G2
    G2 -- reject --> S
    G2 -- approve --> E

    E --> Gen
    Gen --> Ev
    Ev -- fail --> Gen
    Ev -- pass --> TD
    TD --> E

    E -- blocked --> RP
    RP -- resolved --> E
    RP -- escalate --> HG
    HG --> E

    E -- phase complete --> PG
    PG -- advance --> E
    PG -- reopen --> R
    PG -- done --> C
